item.title: Patty Murray biograph
item.description: Senator Patty Murray Biograph Senator Patricia Lynn Murray (D) is an American educator and politician. She has been serving as a senior U.S. Senator from Washington under the Democrats since 1993. She also served as a member of the Washing State Senate from 1989 to 1993. Murray was born in Brothel, Washington, on Oct 11, 1950. She was born to an accountant mom and a war veteran dad. As a teenager, Murray and her family struggled financially.
